                        <interp inst="t18370403-name-1084" type="given" value="HECTOR"></interp>HECTOR ESSEX</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker, and live in Upper-street, Isling<lb></lb>ton. This waistcoat was pawned, on the 21st of March, by the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370403-name-1085" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18370403-name-1085" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
